{
  "name": "魔能爪刺青 Eldritch Claw Tattoo",
  "type": "equipment",
  "img": "icons/tools/scribal/burnisher-tooth.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"wordsection1\">覆蓋區域：半條肢體或一整塊頭皮</p><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"wordsection1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">這個繪有爪型或其他鋸齒型圖案的刺</span><span class=\"GramE\">青需要</span>用一根特殊的針製作。 <br /><em><strong>刺青同調。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">同調此物品時，你需要將針持握，並抵在你想要讓刺</span><span class=\"GramE\">青出現</span>的那處面板上。當同調完成時，針頭會化為墨水再變成刺青。若你與刺青的同調結束，刺青會消失，針頭會再次出現在你的位置中。<br /><em><strong>魔法打擊。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">只要該刺青在你的面板上，攻擊對非魔法攻擊具有抗性或免疫的目標時，你的徒手打擊視為魔法攻擊，並且你以徒手打擊發動的攻擊檢定和傷害擲</span><span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>獲得+1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">加值。</span> <br /><span class=\"GramE\"><em><strong>魔能巨</strong></em></span><em><strong>錘。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">作為一個附贈動作，你可以增強刺青</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">分鐘。持續時間內，你每次以武器或徒手打擊發動近戰攻擊時，墨水觸鬚會朝著對方噴射而去，使你可以觸及距離你最遠</span>15<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺的目標。此外，你的近戰攻擊命中時會造成額外</span>1d6<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">力場傷害。使用后，直到下次黎明前，此附贈動作不能再次使用。</span></p></div></div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
